		"description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Super Sledgehammers are powered variants of the regular sledgehammer. Older, pre-War designs were outfitted with kinetic storage devices to increase the impact force, while post-War ones mount a small rocket motor within the hammer&rsquo;s head to accelerate the swing and deliver a heavier blow.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">A Super Sledgehammer can accept one of the following mods which are </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">installed with the Repair skill:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Super Sledge:</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"> Heating Coil, Stun Pack</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
